  "description": "Unknot at very low tangle (0.1) but high feedback (0.88) — the FDN self-entangles through accumulation, not topology. The resonances build and interfere with themselves rather than through knot routing. Triangle LFO sweeps tangle to occasionally approach the trefoil boundary before retreating. Medium rhythmic feel.",
